appName: Car Driving in City - Endless Runner

display_name: Car Driving in City - Endless Runner
display_long_description: Car driving in city is one of the best endless car driving racer game in bulk traffic. Unlike other racing games, you can modify your racer car. While in city traffic driving, to get better points, you either need to speed up or pass other traffic cars closely. Endless driving and racing in luxury car has never been that much fun before. Hold steering wheel and enjoy car driving in in city highway. A real city car driving on endless highway begins with extreme crazy racing with high speed nitro boost. Feed the adrenaline rush with thundering turbo engine with a free racing thrill. This car racer game with freeway racing opportunity. Experience car driving with real racing challenge for endless car driving lovers.
